{"tid":1219790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次唔只係反送中，仲係香港基本法保護戰！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:02:17.000Z","uid":154007,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5fab099b8dfe575f6ffdeb614b9aae9a57000edf","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>呢度問大家一個問題</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你到底想係呢場革命入面得到啲咩</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回逃犯條例？<br />\n<br />\n要向戰犯報仇？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭落台？<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立建國？<br />\n<br />\n中共打輸貿易戰自滅？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要達成以上嘅所有目標<br />\n我地就要認清</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中共用逃犯條例破壞</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立司法管轄權</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">司法管轄權</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係由港英時代遺產，到而家中共殖民仲存在嘅權力</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更重要嘅係，佢係一個國家嘅無形國界</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過咗深圳河嚟到香港，<br />\n你就得到自由世界留落嘅司法制度，<br />\n你嘅錢就受到自由世界保障，<br />\n唔會突然被中共沒收<br />\n呢個係好多蝗蟲落嚟/走資嘅原因<br />\n香港就係獨立司法管轄權先有今日嘅繁榮<br />\n而家中共打貿易戰打到冇錢<br />\n想利用逃犯條例一鋪攞晒香港所有嘢<br />\n將香港變成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅色帝國</strong></span>嘅一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例係要反 但呢個議題始終有一日會完 <br />\n中共之後都會再推出其他惡法令香港變成地獄鬼國<br />\n我建議將「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反送中</span></span></strong>」正名做「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港憲法保衛戰</span></span></span></strong>」<br />\n我認為有以下幾個好處<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>出師名正言順 </strong></span><br />\n我地話反送中 反會俾人負面嘅感覺<br />\n話要保衛香港嘅憲法 保衛呢兩個字係正面嘅<br />\n有助我哋打民意戰<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">永續抗爭</span></strong><br />\n就算今次議題完咗 通過與否 得到嘅士氣都可以繼續維持<br />\n就算你反對中港融合 反對大灣區 都係捍衛緊憲法<br />\n因為保護自己家園嘅司法制度權力同形式係一個永恆嘅抗爭<br />\n尤其係有中共係隔離搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更何況過幾日就係美國表決香港人權法案 大家要撐住等美軍到<br />\n支持到可以講「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">美軍來了我帶路</span></span></strong>」個日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家都唔駛驚被人話港獨</span></strong><br />\n基本法係中共送畀香港嘅小憲法 我地話抗爭捍衛憲法名正言順<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想同大家講<br />\n無論你係邊一派<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再跟大台</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再俾泛民出賣</span></span></strong><br />\n14 16都俾泛民出賣 仲要俾人割席 篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次612都係因為泛民出賣我哋先會出現<br />\n難得今次美國支持我哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔可以令機會斷送係泛民班仆街冚家剷手中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後一次機會啦各位 蘇州過後冇船搭呀</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要建國呀</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最後嘅最後，呢篇嘢嘅credit係陳雲，風火輪轉左五年轉返嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"619b19b94f3083df55d42682be4a192b89db1a72","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a93b5ae7e2389b3179864b040bc6f6e39a97473","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c0fdb3b9840e2f98e6f2eced81aa541b9b0fbf","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"217ae6ebc6b6d64d4c318af8cdef80055016f435","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e2e4a14ec4d1bfec28b18e465343c24a071bd86f","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"bc7b381a48ab3250e347fe7e2e326441305e6ffd","tid":1219790,"uid":154007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"push"}]}